components.templateData:
<ngx-graph [links]="links" [nodes]="nodes" class="chart-container" [layoutSettings]="layoutSettings"
  [draggingEnabled]="false" [enableZoom]="true">
  <ng-template #defsTemplate>
    <svg:marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 -5 10 10" refX="8" refY="0" markerWidth="4" markerHeight="4" orient="auto">
      <svg:path d="M0,-5L10,0L0,5" class="arrow-head" />
    </svg:marker>
  </ng-template>

  <ng-template #nodeTemplate let-node>
    <svg:g class="node" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/xhtml">

      <svg:foreignObject [attr.width]="node.dimension.width" [attr.height]="node.dimension.height">
        <xhtml:div class="cardContainer" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
          style="justify-content: center;display: flex; height: 100%; width: 100%;">
          <app-bubble-with-icon style="margin: auto;" [title]="'asdf'"></app-bubble-with-icon>
        </xhtml:div>
      </svg:foreignObject>
    </svg:g>
  </ng-template>
</ngx-graph>
